description.narrative: In 2019 UNICEF Wash continued its work to ensure improved water, sanitation and hygiene in communities and institutions. Water safety planning ensure follow up and retention in ODF communities. Baseline analysis was performed on the access to WASH in schools showing the need for significantly increased infrastructure improvement and hygiene promotion, especially towards young girls. UNICEF continues to support the private market of handpump spares. repairs and the market forming for sanitation products, The introduction of the new self closing sanitation pan has meant a significant advance on the sanitation ladder and is improving the sanitation norms in the communities. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
